        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:surest.sky@gmail.com">surest.sky@gmail.com</a></p>
        <p><strong>Response Time:</strong> We typically respond within 24-48 hours on business days.</p>
      </div>

      <h2>Reporting Bugs</h2>
      <p>Found a bug or have a suggestion? We'd love to hear from you!</p>
      <p>Please include the following information when reporting an issue:</p>
